## Data Flow Diagram

```mermaid
graph TB
    A[Prompts JSONL] -->|load_prompts| B[80 prompts]
    B -->|batch into 10| C[Batch Processing]
    
    C -->|ModelWrapper.capture_mlp_inputs| D[Forward Pass + Hooks]
    D -->|Extract decision positions| E[MLP Inputs<br/>80×2048 per layer]
    
    F[Pre-trained Transcoders<br/>from HuggingFace] -->|load_transcoder_set| G[TranscoderSet]
    
    E -->|encode| G
    G -->|JumpReLU| H[Sparse Features<br/>80×163840]
    
    H -->|topk k=50| I[Top-K Features<br/>80×50]
    H -->|compute stats| J[Feature Frequencies<br/>163840]
    
    I -->|save| K[top_k_indices.npy<br/>top_k_values.npy]
    J -->|save| L[feature_frequencies.npy]
    E -->|position tracking| M[position_map.json]
    
    K --> N[Layer Directories]
    L --> N
    M --> O[Global Files]
    
    N --> P[Script 06: Attribution]
    O --> P
```

